            . I am a publican, and live in King-street, Covent-garden. I have a 1l. note, No. 56, 456, which I took of the prisoner on the 6th of June, between nine and eleven o'clock at night.</p>
               <p>MR. ERCK. It is mine, and has my hand-writing on it.</p>
